          <div class="callout-label">⚠️ Watch for these red flags</div>
          <p>Watch out for <strong>(a)</strong> unlimited-article plans under $20/mo (you are paying for unedited spun output), <strong>(b)</strong> 12-month contracts with no usage guarantee, and <strong>(c)</strong> tools that promise "writes for you" but only export to clipboard — no CMS publish means it is a draft generator, not blog software.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 id="how-we-tested">How we tested all 10 tools</h2>
        <p>Each tool produced 30 articles in 30 days on the same 30-keyword shortlist, across 4 real SMB sites.</p>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>Sites tested</strong> — 4 SMB blogs (HVAC, dental, SaaS, ecom) at DA 18–32.</li>
          <li><strong>Scope</strong> — 30 articles per tool, 30-day window.</li>
          <li><strong>Measurement</strong> — Originality.ai AI score, Search Console indexation, 90-day Plausible organic delta.</li>
          <li><strong>Total spend</strong> — $1,940 across 10 platforms — 3-month tracking window.</li>
        </ul>

